text: "Heartache All Over the World" is an upbeat song by Elton John and from his 20th studio album Leather Jackets. It was one a poorest efforts by Elton John and reached 45 in the United Kingdom and number 55 in the United States. In Australia it fared much better by making number 7 in the charts. title: Heartache All Over the World
